messages.message: <!here>  now that we have done a couple of eng-all-hands, would love to get feedback on if you all find it useful -- the goal of this meeting was two-fold: [1] keep eng up-to-date with all the key stuff happening in the company (and in other orgs), [2] have a place to debate/discuss things from both technical as well as strategic perspective. let me know if you want anything changed, or there are areas you want me to cover. put your feedback as comments in slack.
